headline: How Is Host Hotels & Resorts' Stock Performance Compared to Other REIT Stocks?
summary: Despite its underperformance compared to other REIT stocks over the past year, Host Hotels & Resorts has observed a notable surge in recent months and analysts remain optimistic about the stock’s prospects.
